What you need to know:  Pons was awarded the Halda Trophy, which honours the world’s greatest co-drivers. The pair went on to claim five more podium finishes in the WRC. Fabrizia also took victory alongside Hannu Mikkola in the American ‘Press-On-Regardless’ rally.“I did get the Halda Trophy as the world’s best co-driver, which was a really great honour for me,” said Pons, a mother of two in an interview with Audi's official Media Centre website last year.